{"tid":1694030,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"由今日開始唔準再叫死黑警或者狗","createTime":"2019-11-05T02:31:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T10:18:59.000Z","uid":61520,"like":40,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"51f639ba3d3fedaddb0cb0fe41bd2245805544f2","tid":1694030,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:31:18.000Z","msg":"全部人同我改叫 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">死曱由</span></span><br />\n依班green object 先係有破壞無建設既<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">曱由</span></span><br />\n<br />\n以後見到依班扑街 同我大聲叫<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">死曱由</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">曱由王-曱近平 下面既曱由就係佢地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">死曱由 死番大灣區啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"232a4a2e7ff953f4d617da26e583b4420544ec33","tid":1694030,"uid":278015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:32:34.000Z","msg":"死曱由<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c774067be04743ef3c921656f3ae9e5d3d4fb8d2","tid":1694030,"uid":249015,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:37:49.000Z","msg":"叫過街老鼠hurt好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0edd7a40de6852c63fc2436fa08acb554891272c","tid":1694030,"uid":38886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c774067be04743ef3c921656f3ae9e5d3d4fb8d2","tid":1694030,"uid":249015,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:37:49.000Z","msg":"叫過街老鼠hurt好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:38:57.000Z","msg":"輪住黎叫"},{"pid":"340b600cdfe4455aafac14b9b9974300dc983219","tid":1694030,"uid":61520,"lik